title: Bobby Gets A Message from Keith Urban + Amy Hired A Dog Whisperer for $80 bucks an hour… + Blake Shelton Tells Us About His Engagement + Remembering Charlie Pride
itunes:title: Bobby Gets A Message from Keith Urban + Amy Hired A Dog Whisperer for $80 bucks an hour… + Blake Shelton Tells Us About His Engagement + Remembering Charlie Pride
description:
Bobby had God ‘Whispered Your Name’ by Keith Urban as his top song of 2020. Keith sent Bobby a really cool message in response! Amy says her dog has been acting unusual so she decided to hire a dog whisperer to see what the issue could be. We talk to Blake Shelton about his engagement, the Voice finale and the holidays. Bobby remembers Charlie Pride who passed away over the weekend.
